text: Coogler is a surname of German origin, and an Americanized version of Kugler. Notable people with the surname include: *J. Gordon Coogler (1865–1901), American poet *L. Scott Coogler (born 1959), American judge *Ryan Coogler (born 1986), American film director, producer and screenwriter ==See also== *T.S. Coogler House ==References== Category:Surnames of German origin
title: Coogler
